title: Awesome Value, Great Location! Reserve this 2 BR Apt. Home Today!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Make Elm Creek Apartments your home today!', 'You will find functional living space and comfort in our one, two and three bedroom apartments.', 'These amazing apartment homes are equipped with a unique open eat in kitchen design which leads to your living area.', 'You will benefit from the ample storage space in this apartment.', 'There is an over-sized closet in your hallway along with a roomy walk in closet included in the master bedroom.', 'Call today and schedule a tour of our outstanding facility and beautiful community!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Professional On-Site Management', '- Entryway Coat Closet*', '- Master-Suite Walk-In Closet (select homes)', '- Ample Counter Top & Cabinet Space', '- Outdoor Community Playground Area', '- Underground Parking Garage Space Included', '- Large Walk-Out Patio Or Private Balcony', '- Near Elm Creek Park Reserve', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'ElmCreek participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-2:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Elmcreek Apartments', '11719 Champlin Drive', 'Champlin, MN, 55316', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '5Pin3IMgYNe']
